Description: Inversion of direction of movement.0 / Inversion Off /oFF: Inversion of direction ofmovement is off1 / Inversion On /on: Inversion of direction ofmovement is onThe limit switch which is reached with a movementin positive direction must be connected to thepositive limit switch input and vice versa.Setting can only be modified if power stage isdisabled.Modified settings become active the next time theproduct is powered on.
Parameter address via fieldbus: CANopen 3006:ChModbus 1560Profibus 1560CIP 106.1.12ModbusTCP 1560EtherCAT 3006:ChPROFINET 1560
